flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B{Readable input file?}
    B -- No --> C[Print usage and exit]
    B -- Yes --> D[Concatenate input files]
    D --> E[Convert uppercase to lowercase]
    E --> F[Split spaces into new lines]
    F --> G[Remove non-letter characters]
    G --> H[Sort words]
    H --> I[Remove duplicates]
    I --> J[Remove comment lines]
    J --> K[Remove blank lines]
    K --> L[Print dictionary list]
    L --> M[Exit]
